            "type": "text",
            "text": "AI tool renewal playbooks combine scenario classification, BATNA development, and a 90-day timeline to systematically reduce the cost of the GenAI tooling portfolio. The over-licensed and competitive scenarios deliver the largest savings and are the most common in enterprise AI portfolios. Success depends on starting the process at T-90, having real utilization data as evidence, developing a credible BATNA with honest switching cost estimates, and tracking outcomes to build organisational negotiation capability over successive renewal cycles."
